io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.rsrc

Enum ResourceDirectoryKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ResourceDirectoryKey>
      • io.github.struppigel.parser.sections.rsrc.ResourceDirectoryKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HeaderKey, FieldOrStructureKey, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ResourceDirectoryKey>

    public enum ResourceDirectoryKey
extends java.lang.Enum<ResourceDirectoryKey>
implements HeaderKey
    Represents the header key of a resource directory table.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      CHARACTERISTICS
      Resource flags.
      MAJOR_VERSION
      The major version number, set by the user.
      MINOR_VERSION
      The minor version number, set by the user.
      NR_OF_ID_ENTRIES
      The number of directory entries immediately following the Name entries
      NR_OF_NAME_ENTRIES
      The number of directory entries immediately following the table that use strings to identify Type, Name, or Language entries (depending on the level of the table).
      TIME_DATE_STAMP
      The time that the resource data was created by the resource compiler.
